## Roger Stringer's GitHub Projects.
I build things. You can play with them.

### Hire Me
I'm available for projects through my company, [Freekrai](http://www.freekrai.net/?ref=rsgh) (@freekrai). Email info@freekrai.net or call +1 (250) 486-1027.

### Support or Contact
The best way to get support is to add issues, fork repos, and add pull requests. You can email me at roger@freekrai.net.
